sudoku.si
Interface VoidMethodInvokable

All Known Implementing Classes:
SudokuApplet, SudokuFrame, SudokuPanel
public interface VoidMethodInvokable

A tagging interface for void method invokables. Implementers of this interface are declaring that they have a void (and no-argument) method that can be invoked on them via reflection.

See Also:
InvokeMethodAction
